Introduction

Jihan is a South Korean singer and dancer under IST Entertainment. She is the Lead Vocalist, Lead Dancer and Visual of the girl group Weeekly.

On May 19, 2023, Jihan was confirmed as a constant in Mnet's survival show, "Queendom Puzzle". The show began airing on June 13, but Jihan was eliminated in the final, her final rank being 10th.
